<subSubSection id="C30A6528FFB3FF81C5BC1E85FC60FC4B" pageId="17" pageNumber="52" type="description">
<paragraph id="8BAF36A3FFB3FF81C5BC1E85FC60FC4B" blockId="17.[174,1127,746,975]" pageId="17" pageNumber="52">
Taxonomic notes. This species was mentioned in the earlier publications as 
<taxonomicName id="4C104D20FFB3FF81C5991F62FEDDFCA3" authorityName="Eversmann" authorityYear="1856" box="[207,351,781,806]" class="Insecta" family="Noctuidae" genus="Polia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="17" pageNumber="52" phylum="Nemertea" rank="species" species="vesperugo">
<emphasis id="B964EAB1FFB3FF81C5991F62FEDDFCA3" box="[207,351,781,806]" italics="true" pageId="17" pageNumber="52">P. vesperugo</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(auct. nec Eversmann, 
<bibRefCitation id="EF814B52FFB3FF81C72A1F63FCD7FCA3" author="HEYDEMANN, F." box="[636,853,780,806]" pageId="17" pageNumber="52" pagination="12 - 33" refId="ref10990" refString="HEYDEMANN, F. (1944): Zur Kenntnis der Gattung Aplecta Guen. und zweiter &quot; Dual Species &quot; inderselben (Lep. Noct.). - Entomologische Zeitung des Entomologischen Vereins zu Stettin 105: 12 - 33." type="journal article" year="1944">HEYDEMANN 1944</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation id="EF814B52FFB3FF81C6361F63FBBCFCA3" author="HACKER, H. &amp; RONKAY, L. &amp; HREBLAY, M." box="[864,1086,780,806]" pageId="17" pageNumber="52" refId="ref10942" refString="HACKER, H., RONKAY, L. &amp; HREBLAY, M. (2002): Hadeninae I. In: FIBIGER, M. (ed.): Noctuidae Europaeae, vol. 4. - Entomological Press, Soro, 456 pp." type="book" year="2002">
HACKER 
<emphasis id="B964EAB1FFB3FF81C6911F62FC7FFCA3" box="[967,1021,780,806]" italics="true" pageId="17" pageNumber="52">et al.</emphasis>
2002
</bibRefCitation>
) or 
<taxonomicName id="4C104D20FFB3FF81C5F81F41FDC3FCCD" authority="(Sheljuzhko, 1933)" baseAuthorityName="Sheljuzhko" baseAuthorityYear="1933" box="[174,577,813,840]" class="Insecta" family="Noctuidae" genus="Polia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="17" pageNumber="52" phylum="Nemertea" rank="species" species="schawerdae">
<emphasis id="B964EAB1FFB3FF81C5F81F41FED2FCC2" box="[174,336,813,839]" italics="true" pageId="17" pageNumber="52">P. schawerdae</emphasis>
(Sheljuzhko, 1933)
</taxonomicName>
. The synonymy with the latter species was established by 
<bibRefCitation id="EF814B52FFB3FF81C4321F20FDC4FCEC" author="VARGA, Z. &amp; RONKAY, G. &amp; RONKAY, L." box="[356,582,847,873]" pageId="17" pageNumber="52" pagination="133 - 160" refId="ref12050" refString="VARGA, Z., RONKAY, G. &amp; RONKAY, L. (2017): Revised taxonomic check list of the Eurasiatic species of the subtribe Poliina (Noctuidae, Noctuinae, Hadenini). - Deutsche Entomologische Zeitschrift 64 (2): 133 - 160. https: // doi. org / 10.3897 / dez. 64.21455" type="journal article" year="2017">
VARGA 
<emphasis id="B964EAB1FFB3FF81C4EA1F3FFE70FCEC" box="[444,498,847,873]" italics="true" pageId="17" pageNumber="52">et al.</emphasis>
(2017)
</bibRefCitation>
. 
<taxonomicName id="4C104D20FFB3FF81C7061F3FFD18FCEC" authorityName="Pungeler" authorityYear="1914" box="[592,666,847,873]" class="Insecta" family="Noctuidae" genus="Polia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="17" pageNumber="52" phylum="Nemertea" rank="species" species="tiefi">
<emphasis id="B964EAB1FFB3FF81C7061F3FFD18FCEC" box="[592,666,847,873]" italics="true" pageId="17" pageNumber="52">P. tiefi</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is widely distributed with some variation in the external appearance in the high mountains of NE 
<collectingCountry id="F3077633FFB3FF81C6981F1EFBE0FC0E" box="[974,1122,881,907]" name="Kazakhstan" pageId="17" pageNumber="52">Kazakhstan</collectingCountry>
, South Siberia and Northern Mongolia (Saur, Tarbagatai, Sayan, Altai, Khangai and Khentij mountains), mostly in the upper mountain taiga zone.
</paragraph>
